## IHash.hash() method

Returns a value's hash code. The contract of this function is: If `IEquiv.equiv` returns `true` for two values, their hash codes MUST also be equal.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
hash(): T;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`T`
